extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hello #{donorName},
  p Congratulations! Your project brief is now ready for review and is live on our platform.
  p
    strong Project Details:
  ul
    li
      strong Title: 
      | #{projectTitle}
    li
      strong Description: 
      | #{projectDescription}
    li
      strong Budget: 
      | #{budget} NGN
    li
      strong Location: 
      | #{state}, #{city}
  p NGOs on our platform will now be able to view your project brief and submit their applications to execute the project.
  p You can track applications and manage your project directly from your donor dashboard.
  p Thank you for using GivingBack to make a positive impact!
